<span class="art-postdateicon">Published: Tuesday, 31 March 2020 17:41</span> | <span class="art-postauthoricon">Written by Steve Acton</span> | <a href="/parents-students/14-featured/1133-covid-19-update-3-31-20?tmpl=component&amp;print=1&amp;layout=default" title="Print article &lt; COVID-19 Update 3-31-20 &gt;" onclick="window.open(this.href,'win2','status=no,toolbar=no,scrollbars=yes,titlebar=no,menubar=no,resizable=yes,width=640,height=480,directories=no,location=no'); return false;" rel="nofollow">			<span class="icon-print" aria-hidden="true"></span>
